+# 0231 code rule — Scheduler EventBus supervisor source
+
+`0231` may only connect Scheduler-originated EventBus events to the existing
+passive supervisor sink.
+
+Required:
+
+```text
+Scheduler = upstream orchestration authority
+EventBus = canonical event transport
+PassiveSupervisorSink = downstream-only observer
+CellularState/snapshot = passive projection
+```
+
+Forbidden:
+
+```text
+Scheduler.run() is forbidden
+Scheduler imports are forbidden
+Scheduler handler dispatch by the supervisor is forbidden
+new EventBus implementation is forbidden
+status.json/events.jsonl as the normal path is forbidden
+proxy control is forbidden
+SHM writes are forbidden
+policy decisions are forbidden
+SQL/Qdrant/GitHub writes are forbidden
+non-stdlib dependencies are forbidden
+```
+
+The implementation must reuse the existing passive supervisor module and keep
+snapshot/audit outputs optional.
